title: Watch: Hina Khan Dancing Like There’s No Tomorrow
text:
Swagata Dam Mar . 7 . 2017 Hina Khan | Source: Instagram | 
After quitting the daily soap, Yeh Rishta Kya Kehlata Hai , Hina Khan is Akshara no more and she’s making the most of her free time. The gorgeous actress recently got a stunning photoshoot done. You can check out the pictures here . And now, Hina has posted a dance video of herself where she’s rehearsing for an upcoming performance. See her grooving like there’s no tomorrow. A post shared by Hina Khan (@realhinakhan) on Mar 6, 2017 at 8:31am PST 
She sure looks like she’s having a lot of fun! 7
